description:
Affordable organic "artisan" burgers. I'm a huge fan of bison so I'll try any spot that has some. Typical crowd: yuppies from the surrounding area, but don't let that deter you. (or attract you) 

Get the fry-fecta!!

Would get 5 stars if they offered regular soda fountain drinks instead of their homemade sodas. Sometimes I just want a damned coke :{
